# No Cursor commit attribution

Never add any of the following to commit messages, PR descriptions, or git trailers:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `Made-with: Cursor`
- Any `--trailer` flag that adds Cursor attribution

When committing, use plain messages only (`git commit -m "..."` or `-F file`).

If attribution was added by the environment, amend it out before finishing the task.
